snippet.title: Clifford the Big Red Dog : Clifford's Phonics
snippet.description:
Clifford the Big Red Dog:  Clifford s Phonics

Clifford is a very big red dog, which sometimes he gets into trouble because of his size or is tempted into trouble by his friends and those he meets. His size, like giants in medieval legends, is inconsistent—he is often shown as being about 25' tall from paws to head, but can appear far larger. Emily Elizabeth gave him a huge amount of love, which caused his big size.
